        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>SALT Deduction Fairness Act </strong></p> <p>This bill increases the limitation on the deduction for state and local taxes to $20,000 for individuals filing a joint tax return. The limitation applies to taxable years 2018 through 2025. </p>]]>
        </text>
